      "id": "PopularPost250157",
      "post_content": "Modern text-splicing technology yields:  \n  \n**Veteran's Voice**  \n![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)  \nEnchantment - Aura  \nEnchant creature  \nEnchanted creature has \"![Tap](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=tap&type=symbol): [Another](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=2991) target creature gets +2/+1 until end of turn.\"  \n  \nThough this archaic version does have the advantage of ignoring summoning sickness...  \nAlso this way it's always a red ability, as opposed to being whatever color the creature is.  \n  \nUgh, I just learned that this had the cleaner, text-splicing template until the Scars of Mirrodin update.   \nIf we can declare that \"![0](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=0&type=symbol)**:** Pay THIS **to** do THAT\" should always be interpreted as \"Pay THIS**:** Do THAT\", why can't we declare that the intent of these old cards was to splice the ability onto the enchanted permanent?",
      "posted_by": "HuntingDrake",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost250157\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Modern text-splicing technology yields:<br/><br/><b>Veteran's Voice</b><br/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/><br/>Enchantment - Aura<br/>Enchant creature<br/>Enchanted creature has \"<img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Tap\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=tap&amp;type=symbol\"/>: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"2991\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=2991\">Another</a> target creature gets +2/+1 until end of turn.\"<br/><br/>Though this archaic version does have the advantage of ignoring summoning sickness...<br/>Also this way it's always a red ability, as opposed to being whatever color the creature is.<br/><br/>Ugh, I just learned that this had the cleaner, text-splicing template until the Scars of Mirrodin update. <br/>If we can declare that \"<img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"0\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=0&amp;type=symbol\"/><b>:</b> Pay THIS <b>to</b> do THAT\" should always be interpreted as \"Pay THIS<b>:</b> Do THAT\", why can't we declare that the intent of these old cards was to splice the ability onto the enchanted permanent?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '250157'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy26712\">HuntingDrake</span>\r\n                                (6/7/2012 3:30:42 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
