    {
      "id": "PopularPost296724",
      "post_content": "The card would be better and more thematic if the card also had \"When Veteran's Voice is put into a graveyard from the battlefield, you may return Veteran's Voice to play enchanting a target creature you control that does not have summoning sickness.\"  \n  \nThat way, the card could be given to any veteran (as in a creature that had been in play). Alternatively, there could be text allowing you to cast the card from your graveyard with flash when a creature you control attacks or blocks.",
      "posted_by": "ThatStunna",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost296724\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">The card would be better and more thematic if the card also had \"When Veteran's Voice is put into a graveyard from the battlefield, you may return Veteran's Voice to play enchanting a target creature you control  that does not have summoning sickness.\"<br/><br/>That way, the card could be given to any veteran (as in a creature that had been in play).  Alternatively, there could be text allowing you to cast the card from your graveyard with flash when a creature you control attacks or blocks.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '296724'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy91915\">ThatStunna</span>\r\n                                (2/1/2013 12:05:29 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"